1
00:00:10,600 --> 00:00:12,000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

2
00:01:06,540 --> 00:01:07,220
[The Eternal Fragrance]

3
00:01:07,220 --> 00:01:11,980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

4
00:01:12,020 --> 00:01:15,140
[Episode 20]

5
00:01:18,800 --> 00:01:19,450
Qin.

6
00:01:20,080 --> 00:01:20,650
Qin.

7
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:21,860
What happened to you?

8
00:01:22,390 --> 00:01:23,730
Did you get beaten up in your dream?

9
00:01:34,880 --> 00:01:35,530
I'm fine.

10
00:01:45,160 --> 00:01:45,700
Trouble!

11
00:01:46,190 --> 00:01:47,650
Demons are breaking the mountain-sea barrier.

12
00:01:48,310 --> 00:01:49,420
Return to the city at once

13
00:01:49,600 --> 00:01:50,420
and guard the people.

14
00:02:42,040 --> 00:02:43,060
The demon beast Qiongqi.

15
00:03:13,640 --> 00:03:15,740
[Qiongqi]
I'm Qiongqi. Greetings, My Lord.

16
00:03:18,670 --> 00:03:19,250
My Lord,

17
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:20,500
you've finally returned.

18
00:03:21,830 --> 00:03:22,940
Is the lord you mentioned

19
00:03:24,320 --> 00:03:25,410
the Demon Lord Yecha?

20
00:03:25,870 --> 00:03:27,300
Word spread that you reappeared on the White Cliff.

21
00:03:27,590 --> 00:03:28,220
The whole demon clan

22
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,780
longs for your arrival.

23
00:03:30,200 --> 00:03:31,650
After five centuries of exile and humiliation,

24
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:34,130
we've dreamed of your return

25
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,250
to restore our demon clan.

26
00:03:41,270 --> 00:03:42,300
I'm not your Demon Lord.

27
00:03:43,590 --> 00:03:44,500
Leave Duanming City

28
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:46,340
with your followers at once.

29
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:48,570
But the Guardians ordered...

30
00:03:52,200 --> 00:03:53,020
Yes, My Lord.

31
00:04:27,910 --> 00:04:28,570
Thank you.

32
00:04:50,710 --> 00:04:51,330
Tongzhou.

33
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:52,130
Let's go.

34
00:05:06,150 --> 00:05:06,770
Uncle.

35
00:05:17,080 --> 00:05:17,770
What's this?

36
00:05:19,320 --> 00:05:20,300
The Four Symbols Divine Fire Formation.

37
00:06:08,960 --> 00:06:09,450
Medicine.

38
00:06:09,760 --> 00:06:10,420
Here.

39
00:06:12,910 --> 00:06:13,500
Are you alright?

40
00:06:14,200 --> 00:06:14,860
I'm fine.

41
00:06:18,910 --> 00:06:19,570
Move!

42
00:06:21,030 --> 00:06:21,660
Get up!

43
00:06:21,830 --> 00:06:23,130
Get up right now, you beast!

44
00:06:25,790 --> 00:06:26,660
Are you seeking death?

45
00:06:32,320 --> 00:06:33,540
- Get up. - Are you hurt?

46
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:37,690
Who's there?

47
00:06:39,880 --> 00:06:40,810
It's just a cub.

48
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:42,010
Doesn't seem to have killed anyone.

49
00:06:42,030 --> 00:06:42,660
Why slay it?

50
00:06:44,320 --> 00:06:45,300
You

51
00:06:45,560 --> 00:06:47,420
spared that little beast last time!

52
00:06:47,790 --> 00:06:48,210
You...

53
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:49,180
All of you

54
00:06:49,560 --> 00:06:51,100
are in league with the monster beast.

55
00:06:52,320 --> 00:06:53,540
Bully the weak

56
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:54,450
and twist the truth, huh?

57
00:06:54,790 --> 00:06:57,180
Duanming City used to live in peace.

58
00:06:57,470 --> 00:06:58,570
Ever since you showed up,

59
00:06:58,960 --> 00:06:59,770
either the barrier breaks

60
00:06:59,790 --> 00:07:00,770
or demon beasts run amok.

61
00:07:00,960 --> 00:07:02,370
How can you deny you're spies?

62
00:07:02,830 --> 00:07:04,010
What do you mean?

63
00:07:04,520 --> 00:07:05,450
We've worked tirelessly

64
00:07:05,470 --> 00:07:06,500
to subdue monsters and calm chaos.

65
00:07:06,790 --> 00:07:08,130
How dare you slander us?

66
00:07:08,640 --> 00:07:10,690
Everyone knows Mountain Sect's disciples are crafty.

67
00:07:11,200 --> 00:07:12,690
Chances are, you came to the East Sea

68
00:07:13,200 --> 00:07:15,660
with malicious intent to stir trouble.

69
00:07:15,880 --> 00:07:16,690
Watch your words!

70
00:07:16,710 --> 00:07:17,740
You slander us out of thin air!

71
00:07:17,790 --> 00:07:19,010
This is the Sea Sect's territory.

72
00:07:19,030 --> 00:07:19,890
Leave at once!

73
00:07:23,880 --> 00:07:24,620
Silence!

74
00:07:32,710 --> 00:07:33,980
Among these captured monster beasts,

75
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:36,100
some are spirit companions raised by the Sea Sect.

76
00:07:36,640 --> 00:07:37,660
There is a hidden truth behind this chaos.

77
00:07:38,320 --> 00:07:39,660
The Guangsheng Faction only detains them,

78
00:07:40,200 --> 00:07:41,180
with no authority to pass judgment.

79
00:07:44,200 --> 00:07:46,770
Mr. Shen and the immortal elders haven't looked into this yet.

80
00:07:47,270 --> 00:07:48,940
You're trying to kill them to cover up the truth, huh?

81
00:07:49,880 --> 00:07:50,620
Fine, forget it.

82
00:07:50,880 --> 00:07:51,890
Let's go.

83
00:07:52,790 --> 00:07:53,660
Move, follow me.

84
00:07:54,640 --> 00:07:55,100
Come.

85
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:56,570
Go.

86
00:07:57,150 --> 00:07:57,810
Hurry up!

87
00:07:58,200 --> 00:07:58,660
Faster!

88
00:08:00,270 --> 00:08:00,860
Quick!

89
00:08:03,790 --> 00:08:04,420
Be careful.

90
00:08:06,880 --> 00:08:07,570
Behave yourselves.

91
00:08:07,760 --> 00:08:08,210
Hurry.

92
00:08:08,880 --> 00:08:09,690
I'll follow them to watch them,

93
00:08:10,030 --> 00:08:11,060
in case they stir up more trouble.

94
00:08:18,890 --> 00:08:20,080
[Duanming City Inn]

95
00:08:20,080 --> 00:08:22,300
You know that cultivating the Xuanhua Sacred Fire

96
00:08:22,390 --> 00:08:23,740
requires severing all mortal affection.

97
00:08:24,470 --> 00:08:26,300
Yet only a few days after arriving in Duanming City,

98
00:08:26,910 --> 00:08:28,300
your spirit sense has sustained damage,

99
00:08:28,470 --> 00:08:29,660
and a heart tribulation looms over you.

100
00:08:30,440 --> 00:08:32,010
Is it because of Jiang Lifei?

101
00:08:33,390 --> 00:08:34,370
I let my guard down for a moment.

102
00:08:34,910 --> 00:08:35,740
It has nothing to do with her.

103
00:08:36,710 --> 00:08:38,970
Besides, she's far stronger now.

104
00:08:39,110 --> 00:08:39,940
Her cultivation has advanced greatly,

105
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:41,450
and she saved me on Fanghu Island.

106
00:08:44,470 --> 00:08:45,300
Tongzhou,

107
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:49,690
the Xuanhua Sacred Fire is the Hua Sect's supreme technique.

108
00:08:50,160 --> 00:08:52,450
No one has mastered it in hundreds of years,

109
00:08:53,920 --> 00:08:55,180
not even me.

110
00:08:57,320 --> 00:08:59,610
If you cannot cast aside personal desires

111
00:08:59,630 --> 00:09:00,690
and master the Sacred Fire,

112
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:04,140
how will you lead Xingzheng Hall

113
00:09:04,630 --> 00:09:07,570
and fulfill the grand plan to secure Yue's realm?

114
00:09:09,040 --> 00:09:10,420
I'll master the supreme technique.

115
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,210
You have my word.

116
00:09:14,660 --> 00:09:15,140
But

117
00:09:17,110 --> 00:09:18,330
I'll never give up Jiang Lifei.

118
00:09:18,830 --> 00:09:20,020
In your life,

119
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:21,730
you gain only after you let go.

120
00:09:21,980 --> 00:09:22,900
The immortal path is lonely.

121
00:09:22,920 --> 00:09:24,140
How can you have both?

122
00:09:24,580 --> 00:09:25,380
Whether I can have both,

123
00:09:26,230 --> 00:09:27,300
I'll have my own judgment.

124
00:09:29,040 --> 00:09:30,810
No need to lecture me

125
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:32,060
over and over.

126
00:09:34,470 --> 00:09:35,300
Very well.

127
00:09:38,590 --> 00:09:39,780
If you insist on this foolish path,

128
00:09:40,110 --> 00:09:40,690
so be it.

129
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:45,690
I'll wait for the day you hit a dead end

130
00:09:46,470 --> 00:09:48,380
and damage your cultivation.

131
00:09:50,540 --> 00:09:51,180
Tongzhou,

132
00:09:51,630 --> 00:09:52,690
here's the antidote to the monster poison...

133
00:09:54,400 --> 00:09:55,210
Mr. Xuanshan.

134
00:10:08,820 --> 00:10:10,090
He's so furious.

135
00:10:14,590 --> 00:10:16,140
Still because of the mirage dream?

136
00:10:17,300 --> 00:10:18,330
What did you see?

137
00:10:19,180 --> 00:10:20,180
Are you still under its influence?

138
00:10:23,060 --> 00:10:24,490
All those illusions are fake.

139
00:10:24,980 --> 00:10:26,380
Dwelling on them, and you'll lose yourself.

140
00:10:26,420 --> 00:10:27,020
I'm not dwelling on it.

141
00:10:29,110 --> 00:10:29,970
You don't understand.

142
00:10:31,060 --> 00:10:31,850
Don't understand?

143
00:10:32,340 --> 00:10:34,330
Because I don't dwell on painful memories.

144
00:10:34,990 --> 00:10:36,300
Dreams show the opposite of reality.

145
00:10:36,560 --> 00:10:37,490
Try to look on the bright side,

146
00:10:37,680 --> 00:10:38,780
and they might be a good sign.

147
00:10:40,420 --> 00:10:41,210
A good sign?

148
00:10:42,750 --> 00:10:43,420
Think about it.

149
00:10:43,870 --> 00:10:44,780
The illusion laid out

150
00:10:44,820 --> 00:10:46,260
all your deepest fears,

151
00:10:46,470 --> 00:10:48,180
so you can avoid them in the real world.

152
00:10:49,340 --> 00:10:51,090
At the very least,

153
00:10:51,110 --> 00:10:52,660
you won't feel as helpless as you did in the illusion.

154
00:10:55,750 --> 00:10:56,330
Lifei,

155
00:10:58,350 --> 00:11:00,900
if one day a great disaster befalls me,

156
00:11:01,510 --> 00:11:02,180
or

157
00:11:03,180 --> 00:11:04,380
I lose everything

158
00:11:04,940 --> 00:11:05,690
and am left all alone,

159
00:11:06,940 --> 00:11:07,940
would you abandon me?

160
00:11:08,940 --> 00:11:09,940
Your Highness, do not abandon us,

161
00:11:09,980 --> 00:11:11,090
your friends.

162
00:11:25,100 --> 00:11:25,810
How's Tongzhou?

163
00:11:28,830 --> 00:11:29,490
He's alright,

164
00:11:30,340 --> 00:11:31,570
just acting a little strange.

165
00:11:32,990 --> 00:11:34,660
Probably the mirage dream scared him badly.

166
00:11:37,510 --> 00:11:38,140
By the way,

167
00:11:38,710 --> 00:11:40,490
did you catch demon beast Qiongqi?

168
00:11:42,060 --> 00:11:44,210
It got away.

169
00:11:45,420 --> 00:11:46,690
If it escaped your grasp,

170
00:11:47,230 --> 00:11:48,780
it must be extremely powerful.

171
00:11:50,590 --> 00:11:53,020
I wonder how many demon beasts are in the city.

172
00:12:02,420 --> 00:12:04,140
You are fiery

173
00:12:04,340 --> 00:12:06,180
and passionate.

174
00:12:06,220 --> 00:12:07,210
Your cultivation

175
00:12:07,300 --> 00:12:09,260
will surely be fraught with hardships.

176
00:12:09,470 --> 00:12:11,420
All love, hatred, grudges, entanglements,

177
00:12:11,460 --> 00:12:12,570
and the bustling mortal world

178
00:12:12,590 --> 00:12:14,180
will stoke an unquenchable inner flame.

179
00:12:14,300 --> 00:12:15,660
If you cannot let go,

180
00:12:15,830 --> 00:12:17,210
how can you make progress?

181
00:12:18,590 --> 00:12:19,300
Tongzhou.

182
00:12:20,870 --> 00:12:21,570
Lifei.

183
00:12:42,710 --> 00:12:43,690
Dwelling on them,

184
00:12:43,710 --> 00:12:44,690
and you'll lose yourself.

185
00:12:47,110 --> 00:12:48,180
It is a fleeting dream,

186
00:12:48,510 --> 00:12:49,300
all fake.

187
00:12:49,830 --> 00:12:50,610
Let it go.

188
00:12:57,280 --> 00:12:57,850
Lifei.

189
00:13:19,350 --> 00:13:19,850
Speak!

190
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:21,690
Who ordered you to stir up trouble?

191
00:13:22,470 --> 00:13:24,970
You humans are selfish and hypocritical.

192
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:26,660
You oppress the monster clan

193
00:13:27,040 --> 00:13:28,300
and slaughter us at will.

194
00:13:28,800 --> 00:13:30,060
We only fled for our lives.

195
00:13:30,280 --> 00:13:31,540
What's wrong with that?

196
00:13:31,800 --> 00:13:33,210
What's wrong with that?

197
00:13:48,990 --> 00:13:51,610
So it's possessed by the demon clan.

198
00:13:53,400 --> 00:13:53,970
Speak!

199
00:13:54,590 --> 00:13:55,140
Monster,

200
00:13:56,230 --> 00:13:57,940
who is your demon leader?

201
00:13:58,680 --> 00:13:59,610
Old fool.

202
00:14:00,040 --> 00:14:01,210
The Demon Lord has returned.

203
00:14:01,510 --> 00:14:02,970
The Guardians' schemes are flawless.

204
00:14:03,350 --> 00:14:05,810
Soon we'll conquer the Central Plains

205
00:14:06,040 --> 00:14:08,300
and slay every last one of you.

206
00:14:13,920 --> 00:14:15,210
Which Guardian?

207
00:14:16,280 --> 00:14:18,300
Are they hiding in the city now?

208
00:14:24,510 --> 00:14:25,660
Five centuries ago,

209
00:14:25,990 --> 00:14:28,970
I fought two Guardians of the demon clan.

210
00:14:29,280 --> 00:14:30,570
They were extremely crafty.

211
00:14:31,230 --> 00:14:32,490
Whichever one has sneaked in,

212
00:14:33,040 --> 00:14:34,810
they will prove a deadly foe.

213
00:14:36,680 --> 00:14:37,300
Mr. Shen,

214
00:14:37,710 --> 00:14:39,730
we can't question every

215
00:14:39,750 --> 00:14:40,540
captured monster beast.

216
00:14:40,920 --> 00:14:41,730
In my opinion,

217
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:43,420
we may execute all of them together

218
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:44,300
to eliminate future threats.

219
00:14:46,920 --> 00:14:47,490
Lifei!

220
00:14:48,710 --> 00:14:49,330
Lifei!

221
00:14:50,830 --> 00:14:51,450
It's terrible!

222
00:14:51,920 --> 00:14:52,900
Elder Cuixuan has ordered

223
00:14:52,990 --> 00:14:54,940
that all captured monster beasts must be killed.

224
00:14:57,110 --> 00:14:58,260
Did they find the demon leader?

225
00:14:58,470 --> 00:14:59,780
Why kill the monster clan suddenly?

226
00:15:01,870 --> 00:15:03,780
Last night, I went to the Guangsheng Faction's prison

227
00:15:04,280 --> 00:15:06,260
to make sure they wouldn't kill the spirits.

228
00:15:06,750 --> 00:15:08,060
But when I came back this morning,

229
00:15:08,440 --> 00:15:10,020
Luo Chengji's disciples passed down the order

230
00:15:10,510 --> 00:15:12,380
to transfer all monster beasts to the shore

231
00:15:12,680 --> 00:15:13,610
and kill them all,

232
00:15:13,870 --> 00:15:14,690
none spared.

233
00:15:23,830 --> 00:15:24,540
Deng,

234
00:15:25,800 --> 00:15:26,570
what are you doing?

235
00:15:27,560 --> 00:15:28,210
Step out here!

236
00:15:38,400 --> 00:15:40,810
You're hiding a spirit right under the elder's nose.

237
00:15:41,350 --> 00:15:42,420
Are you seeking death?

238
00:15:44,350 --> 00:15:45,900
I saved this little one before.

239
00:15:46,160 --> 00:15:47,610
It risked its life to save me yesterday

240
00:15:47,920 --> 00:15:49,380
and is sharing key information with us.

241
00:15:51,960 --> 00:15:54,490
That day, after Lifei saved me,

242
00:15:54,960 --> 00:15:55,810
I planned to head back

243
00:15:55,830 --> 00:15:57,780
to my homeland, Yingcui Island, with my elders.

244
00:15:58,040 --> 00:15:59,210
But before we left the city,

245
00:15:59,440 --> 00:16:01,140
all the spirit beasts around suddenly went berserk,

246
00:16:01,470 --> 00:16:02,850
and my elders lost their minds too.

247
00:16:03,230 --> 00:16:04,380
I tried to hold them back,

248
00:16:04,510 --> 00:16:05,690
yet they acted as if they didn't know me

249
00:16:05,710 --> 00:16:06,690
and even tried to kill me.

250
00:16:06,870 --> 00:16:07,810
Terrified,

251
00:16:07,830 --> 00:16:08,780
I hid myself away,

252
00:16:09,110 --> 00:16:10,490
and that's when I met Lifei.

253
00:16:12,710 --> 00:16:14,420
Spirit companions may have faint power,

254
00:16:14,710 --> 00:16:16,140
yet they possess some cultivation.

255
00:16:16,590 --> 00:16:18,490
Why are they controlled by the demon clan so easily?

256
00:16:23,750 --> 00:16:24,450
Before they lost control,

257
00:16:24,800 --> 00:16:26,570
did you eat or drink anything?

258
00:16:27,230 --> 00:16:29,610
To avoid being captured again by the Guangsheng Faction,

259
00:16:29,960 --> 00:16:31,060
we didn't even have time to eat.

260
00:16:31,230 --> 00:16:33,140
They drank water from a pond along the way.

261
00:16:33,560 --> 00:16:34,450
I had a mouth wound

262
00:16:35,080 --> 00:16:36,060
and dared not touch the water.

263
00:16:37,400 --> 00:16:38,330
Now it all makes sense.

264
00:16:38,870 --> 00:16:39,850
I was wondering

265
00:16:40,400 --> 00:16:42,140
how the demon clan could seize

266
00:16:42,350 --> 00:16:44,060
all the monster beasts in the city overnight

267
00:16:44,080 --> 00:16:46,610
under the immortal elders' noses.

268
00:16:46,830 --> 00:16:48,180
That would only alert us.

269
00:16:50,630 --> 00:16:52,020
There's only one explanation.

270
00:16:54,320 --> 00:16:55,450
The water source is poisoned.

271
00:16:55,560 --> 00:16:57,090
Yeah, they poisoned the water supply.

272
00:17:06,710 --> 00:17:07,850
I've asked Gelin.

273
00:17:08,230 --> 00:17:09,730
All underground water in Duanming City

274
00:17:09,750 --> 00:17:10,820
connects to this freshwater lake.

275
00:17:11,310 --> 00:17:12,290
If someone wants to poison the water,

276
00:17:12,510 --> 00:17:13,730
this place will be the perfect spot.

277
00:17:34,710 --> 00:17:35,450
They're from the Guangsheng Faction.

278
00:17:36,440 --> 00:17:36,940
Mr. Shi,

279
00:17:37,310 --> 00:17:38,690
I've spread all the sea salt.

280
00:17:39,200 --> 00:17:40,860
After killing every monster beast tomorrow morning,

281
00:17:41,310 --> 00:17:42,660
we'll strip their hides

282
00:17:42,680 --> 00:17:43,620
and cure their flesh.

283
00:17:43,990 --> 00:17:46,380
Not a single hair will go to waste, I promise you.

284
00:17:46,960 --> 00:17:48,420
Seems that the man told me the truth.

285
00:17:49,270 --> 00:17:50,340
Wait till you return to tally your gold.

286
00:17:50,710 --> 00:17:51,180
Let's go.

287
00:17:52,160 --> 00:17:52,620
What if

288
00:17:52,840 --> 00:17:54,100
that old fool changes his mind

289
00:17:54,230 --> 00:17:55,050
and calls off the slaughter?

290
00:17:55,600 --> 00:17:56,180
He won't.

291
00:17:56,600 --> 00:17:57,900
The immortal sects mean to bait someone out,

292
00:17:57,920 --> 00:17:59,250
so they'll kill without mercy.

293
00:17:59,600 --> 00:18:00,250
Hurry, let's go.

294
00:18:08,070 --> 00:18:09,250
Spirit-Releasing Antidote Powder.

295
00:18:11,310 --> 00:18:12,770
It's Shi Chengtian's doing, just as expected.

296
00:18:13,750 --> 00:18:14,620
I'm going to Mr. Shen.

297
00:18:16,680 --> 00:18:17,140
Don't bother.

298
00:18:17,880 --> 00:18:18,690
To them,

299
00:18:19,310 --> 00:18:20,140
the truth means nothing.

300
00:18:21,920 --> 00:18:22,660
The elders know full well what caused

301
00:18:23,310 --> 00:18:25,010
the monster beasts to lose control.

302
00:18:26,270 --> 00:18:27,530
They're using it to eliminate all non-human creatures

303
00:18:27,960 --> 00:18:28,730
and future threats for good.

304
00:18:30,230 --> 00:18:31,140
All lives are precious.

305
00:18:31,710 --> 00:18:32,380
They have no right to decide

306
00:18:32,400 --> 00:18:33,730
the fate of these innocent monster beasts.

307
00:18:35,640 --> 00:18:36,490
As the monster beasts ran amok,

308
00:18:37,400 --> 00:18:39,210
slaying them is what everyone wants.

309
00:18:39,840 --> 00:18:40,900
If you speak up for them,

310
00:18:41,340 --> 00:18:42,100
be ready

311
00:18:42,750 --> 00:18:44,210
to openly stand against the immortal sects.

312
00:18:44,960 --> 00:18:45,690
Do you understand?

313
00:18:46,880 --> 00:18:47,420
I do.

314
00:18:48,470 --> 00:18:50,050
At worst, I'll be barred from returning to Wuyue Court.

315
00:18:51,070 --> 00:18:52,490
If they can't tell right from wrong

316
00:18:52,510 --> 00:18:53,290
and kill the innocent,

317
00:18:53,920 --> 00:18:55,380
I won't care to remain their disciple.

318
00:18:55,990 --> 00:18:56,660
In that case,

319
00:18:56,960 --> 00:18:58,050
we can return to the Chufeng Academy.

320
00:18:58,550 --> 00:18:59,180
Master...

321
00:19:00,270 --> 00:19:00,860
Mr. Hu

322
00:19:01,400 --> 00:19:02,970
and Mr. Zuo Qiu will take us in.

323
00:19:04,600 --> 00:19:05,210
Lifei,

324
00:19:05,880 --> 00:19:06,660
count me in, too!

325
00:19:07,160 --> 00:19:08,010
Count me in, too!

326
00:19:10,030 --> 00:19:11,620
Don't get mixed up in this.

327
00:19:13,160 --> 00:19:14,100
How can I be your senior

328
00:19:14,270 --> 00:19:15,660
and stand aside?

329
00:19:16,600 --> 00:19:17,970
Besides, what are you off to do?

330
00:19:18,840 --> 00:19:20,690
Save all living beings!

331
00:19:21,120 --> 00:19:23,250
It's such a meritorious deed.

332
00:19:23,680 --> 00:19:27,050
I might even ascend to immortality from this.

333
00:19:27,510 --> 00:19:28,250
You must count me in.

334
00:19:31,200 --> 00:19:31,940
This journey will be dangerous,

335
00:19:32,880 --> 00:19:33,660
so you may back out at any time

336
00:19:34,640 --> 00:19:35,210
if you regret it.

337
00:19:38,160 --> 00:19:39,420
- I'll never regret it.
- I'll never regret it.

338
00:19:45,120 --> 00:19:46,250
Everyone, good work out there.

339
00:19:46,790 --> 00:19:48,490
Mr. Shi sends his regards.

340
00:19:56,440 --> 00:19:57,210
It didn't work at all.

341
00:20:03,660 --> 00:20:04,490
I knew it.

342
00:20:04,990 --> 00:20:05,730
Mr. Dongyang refined

343
00:20:05,750 --> 00:20:07,580
this drug from sleep-inducing bugs,

344
00:20:07,620 --> 00:20:08,820
so it can knock them all out.

345
00:20:09,700 --> 00:20:10,140
Go.

346
00:20:14,710 --> 00:20:15,820
Wuyue Court's restriction spell.

347
00:20:16,460 --> 00:20:17,770
What do we do now?

348
00:20:18,360 --> 00:20:19,180
What can we do?

349
00:20:20,180 --> 00:20:20,860
I know how to break it.

350
00:20:22,070 --> 00:20:22,580
Then...

351
00:20:24,900 --> 00:20:25,730
All arts converge as one;

352
00:20:25,940 --> 00:20:26,730
break the formation and reveal the spirit.

353
00:20:30,310 --> 00:20:31,770
You've got real skill.

354
00:20:31,790 --> 00:20:32,490
Naturally.

355
00:20:32,900 --> 00:20:34,730
Since I was taken as my master's personal disciple at three,

356
00:20:35,030 --> 00:20:36,420
I've tinkered with these formations for over a decade.

357
00:20:36,510 --> 00:20:37,380
Child's play for me.

358
00:20:38,550 --> 00:20:38,940
Let's go.

359
00:20:38,990 --> 00:20:39,420
Hurry.

360
00:20:59,310 --> 00:21:01,100
As the mirage poison lingers in your body for ages,

361
00:21:02,750 --> 00:21:04,450
your spirit roots are damaged now.

362
00:21:06,600 --> 00:21:07,820
It may take a decade

363
00:21:08,900 --> 00:21:11,770
to fully mend them.

364
00:21:13,550 --> 00:21:14,660
Darn it.

365
00:21:15,230 --> 00:21:16,140
I'm incompetent

366
00:21:17,620 --> 00:21:19,100
and have troubled you greatly.

367
00:21:19,790 --> 00:21:21,580
Focus solely on recuperating for now.

368
00:21:21,940 --> 00:21:22,580
Once we return,

369
00:21:23,790 --> 00:21:26,530
I'll have Dongyang tend to your conditioning carefully.

370
00:21:27,180 --> 00:21:28,100
Thank you, Master.

371
00:21:28,940 --> 00:21:29,580
Master,

372
00:21:30,270 --> 00:21:31,250
during our time on Fanghu Island,

373
00:21:31,470 --> 00:21:32,660
I discovered that Jiang Lifei...

374
00:21:37,460 --> 00:21:38,770
There's a jailbreak rescue!

375
00:21:43,510 --> 00:21:44,250
Halt!

376
00:21:45,230 --> 00:21:47,180
You should guard the outside.

377
00:21:47,310 --> 00:21:48,420
Why have you come in?

378
00:21:48,860 --> 00:21:49,770
Any more drugs left?

379
00:21:49,790 --> 00:21:50,580
I've given you all of it.

380
00:21:52,660 --> 00:21:54,180
I came inside to relieve myself

381
00:21:54,460 --> 00:21:55,180
and will head out right away.

382
00:21:56,660 --> 00:21:57,420
- You... - He's far too strong.

383
00:21:57,460 --> 00:21:58,530
I'll fetch reinforcements. Hold him off.

384
00:21:58,550 --> 00:21:59,180
What a fair-weather friend.

385
00:22:00,070 --> 00:22:01,490
Are you also here to relieve yourself?

386
00:22:03,990 --> 00:22:05,690
I came along with him. I'm leaving.

387
00:22:05,990 --> 00:22:06,900
Jiang Lifei.

388
00:22:12,990 --> 00:22:15,290
You have sharp eyes and saw

389
00:22:15,510 --> 00:22:17,530
right through my disguise at once.

390
00:22:18,940 --> 00:22:20,450
Why are you dressed like this?

391
00:22:23,420 --> 00:22:25,820
I heard the monster beast chaos

392
00:22:25,860 --> 00:22:27,450
was stirred up by demon spies.

393
00:22:28,220 --> 00:22:29,290
So I thought

394
00:22:29,310 --> 00:22:30,100
if I dressed like this,

395
00:22:30,120 --> 00:22:31,620
I could capture and question a monster beast,

396
00:22:31,940 --> 00:22:33,250
so I could help you capture

397
00:22:33,270 --> 00:22:34,620
demon spies ahead of time.

398
00:22:35,270 --> 00:22:38,010
She is cunning and will become a grave threat.

399
00:22:42,160 --> 00:22:43,100
He's trying to kill me!

400
00:22:44,420 --> 00:22:45,690
I... I have

401
00:22:46,600 --> 00:22:47,690
a terrible stomachache.

402
00:22:47,710 --> 00:22:49,290
May I step aside for a moment?

403
00:22:49,900 --> 00:22:50,530
Stomachache?

404
00:22:50,900 --> 00:22:52,450
Then let me check your pulse.

405
00:22:59,180 --> 00:23:01,140
I'm sacrificing myself to save them!

406
00:23:01,620 --> 00:23:03,730
Xiuyuan, everything rests on you.

407
00:23:22,180 --> 00:23:22,690
Lu.

408
00:23:28,660 --> 00:23:29,290
Clan leader.

409
00:23:31,860 --> 00:23:32,450
Clan leader?

410
00:23:34,270 --> 00:23:35,100
I'm a half-monster.

411
00:23:36,070 --> 00:23:38,660
They are my clansfolk.

412
00:23:39,180 --> 00:23:40,690
I never thought disciples of the immortal sects

413
00:23:40,990 --> 00:23:42,530
would lend a hand to the monster clan.

414
00:23:43,310 --> 00:23:43,940
Lei,

415
00:23:44,990 --> 00:23:45,530
thank you.

416
00:23:48,790 --> 00:23:50,140
The elders will find out soon.

417
00:23:50,940 --> 00:23:51,690
We have to leave at once.

418
00:23:55,550 --> 00:23:56,420
I'm at my limit.

419
00:23:56,710 --> 00:23:57,250
I'll risk everything!

420
00:24:05,230 --> 00:24:06,250
An empty shell.

421
00:24:07,120 --> 00:24:08,100
You were testing me.

422
00:24:08,470 --> 00:24:09,900
You've got some perseverance.

423
00:24:17,310 --> 00:24:18,940
So you really came to rescue them.

424
00:24:21,660 --> 00:24:22,180
Uncle!

425
00:24:24,470 --> 00:24:25,250
Tongzhou?

426
00:24:25,470 --> 00:24:26,050
Uncle,

427
00:24:26,460 --> 00:24:27,420
this whole thing was my idea.

428
00:24:27,700 --> 00:24:28,660
I told Lifei to...

429
00:24:28,860 --> 00:24:30,290
To meet you.

430
00:24:33,750 --> 00:24:34,970
Since His Highness is here,

431
00:24:34,990 --> 00:24:37,010
I'll speak plainly.

432
00:24:37,270 --> 00:24:38,050
What are you doing?

433
00:24:38,660 --> 00:24:40,660
Since His Highness got injured yesterday,

434
00:24:41,070 --> 00:24:42,730
I've been consumed with guilt.

435
00:24:43,220 --> 00:24:44,580
I feared you'd hold a grudge against me.

436
00:24:45,460 --> 00:24:46,530
But His Highness said

437
00:24:47,070 --> 00:24:49,050
you're the kindest,

438
00:24:49,220 --> 00:24:50,690
and you won't hold this against me.

439
00:24:51,220 --> 00:24:52,490
So I ventured here

440
00:24:52,510 --> 00:24:53,690
to explain myself.

441
00:24:53,710 --> 00:24:54,380
Uncle,

442
00:25:00,680 --> 00:25:03,620
please allow us to be cultivation partners.

443
00:25:13,160 --> 00:25:13,690
Lifei,

444
00:25:15,230 --> 00:25:17,690
we've sworn to never abandon one another.

445
00:25:18,440 --> 00:25:20,420
My uncle won't make things hard for you.

446
00:25:21,230 --> 00:25:22,770
Take out the token I gave you.

447
00:25:24,960 --> 00:25:25,730
The Chiyan Stone.

448
00:25:27,710 --> 00:25:29,660
It's here.

449
00:25:30,270 --> 00:25:30,940
Here.

450
00:25:33,400 --> 00:25:35,420
You gave the Zhurong Stone to an outsider?

451
00:25:37,710 --> 00:25:39,620
This is the Zhurong Stone?

452
00:25:40,510 --> 00:25:41,100
Watch out!

453
00:25:44,160 --> 00:25:44,660
Go!

454
00:25:45,600 --> 00:25:46,250
Take care!

455
00:25:47,200 --> 00:25:47,820
Tongzhou,

456
00:25:48,790 --> 00:25:50,420
you dare raise a hand against me?

457
00:25:50,960 --> 00:25:51,660
Calm your anger.

458
00:25:52,680 --> 00:25:53,940
Lifei is no outsider.

459
00:25:54,960 --> 00:25:56,580
She is my cultivation partner who shares life and death with me.

460
00:25:57,640 --> 00:25:59,690
Please grant us your permission.

461
00:26:02,070 --> 00:26:03,490
[Guangsheng Faction]
We're finally out.

462
00:26:04,200 --> 00:26:05,050
Hurry up!

463
00:26:15,710 --> 00:26:17,050
Mere petty trickery.

464
00:26:18,440 --> 00:26:19,050
Reveal your form!

465
00:26:31,070 --> 00:26:32,180
Over there! Chase!

466
00:26:32,310 --> 00:26:33,050
Yes!

467
00:26:49,920 --> 00:26:51,140
They're somewhere nearby.

468
00:27:01,270 --> 00:27:01,900
Mr. Luo,

469
00:27:02,270 --> 00:27:02,770
monster beasts

470
00:27:03,680 --> 00:27:04,690
are trying to kill me.

471
00:27:04,710 --> 00:27:05,380
Where

472
00:27:06,030 --> 00:27:06,770
are they?

473
00:27:07,680 --> 00:27:08,340
Over there!

474
00:27:18,070 --> 00:27:19,140
There's evil spiritual energy

475
00:27:20,960 --> 00:27:22,100
all over you.

476
00:27:27,270 --> 00:27:29,690
I must have gotten monster blood on myself

477
00:27:30,100 --> 00:27:31,140
while fighting them earlier.

478
00:27:31,920 --> 00:27:32,420
Master,

479
00:27:32,510 --> 00:27:33,380
monster beasts are over there!

480
00:27:34,960 --> 00:27:35,820
Right there, let's check it out.

481
00:27:35,990 --> 00:27:37,140
- Go. - Chase!

482
00:27:52,310 --> 00:27:53,100
Dawn is breaking soon.

483
00:27:53,550 --> 00:27:54,620
Are you sure we can get out this way?

484
00:27:54,790 --> 00:27:56,380
There is a secret door under the jar fortress.

485
00:27:56,400 --> 00:27:57,210
We'll make it out for sure.

486
00:28:04,840 --> 00:28:05,420
Leave it to me.

487
00:28:21,840 --> 00:28:22,730
This aura...

488
00:28:27,550 --> 00:28:29,210
Jiang Lifei.

489
00:28:29,230 --> 00:28:29,940
Let them pass.

490
00:28:40,070 --> 00:28:41,180
The trip is dangerous.

491
00:28:42,600 --> 00:28:43,210
Take care.

492
00:28:44,160 --> 00:28:44,660
Will do.

493
00:28:53,550 --> 00:28:53,940
Hurry!

494
00:29:01,920 --> 00:29:03,100
What's going on here?

495
00:29:05,360 --> 00:29:06,250
What happened?

496
00:29:08,710 --> 00:29:09,660
I let my guard down.

497
00:29:10,840 --> 00:29:12,490
They mean to hunt us all down,

498
00:29:12,990 --> 00:29:13,770
leaving none alive.

499
00:29:15,120 --> 00:29:17,580
Fire! Look, there's fire!

500
00:29:18,710 --> 00:29:19,290
Fire!

501
00:29:25,160 --> 00:29:25,940
Everyone, stay calm.

502
00:29:26,880 --> 00:29:27,490
Mr. Lu,

503
00:29:27,600 --> 00:29:28,900
we signed a spirit pact

504
00:29:28,920 --> 00:29:30,490
to live in peace alongside humans.

505
00:29:30,640 --> 00:29:31,770
Why do they seek to slay us,

506
00:29:31,990 --> 00:29:33,530
even leaving our bodies unburied?

507
00:29:33,680 --> 00:29:34,970
The formation won't hold much longer. What to do?

508
00:29:35,270 --> 00:29:35,940
I'll hold them off.

509
00:29:36,400 --> 00:29:38,050
Lead everyone away with Lu Li.

510
00:29:38,750 --> 00:29:39,490
I'm staying here with you.

511
00:29:40,070 --> 00:29:40,580
Lifei.

512
00:29:40,790 --> 00:29:41,730
Don't you act on your own.

513
00:29:42,120 --> 00:29:43,140
The Fragrance Bond still binds us.

514
00:29:43,550 --> 00:29:44,340
We swore

515
00:29:44,790 --> 00:29:46,900
to live and die together, never to abandon each other.

516
00:29:47,230 --> 00:29:48,340
Neither of us shall break that.

517
00:29:54,440 --> 00:29:55,490
[Riyan, Nine-Tailed Fox]
It's so hot in here.

518
00:29:56,710 --> 00:29:58,180
What are you roasting?

519
00:29:59,710 --> 00:30:00,900
Riyan, you've healed up.

520
00:30:01,200 --> 00:30:01,860
Please,

521
00:30:02,120 --> 00:30:03,100
let us get out of here.

522
00:30:04,470 --> 00:30:05,140
I'll give it a shot.

523
00:30:18,880 --> 00:30:19,820
It's the mountain-sea barrier.

524
00:30:21,160 --> 00:30:21,940
I can't break through.

525
00:30:37,710 --> 00:30:39,340
The old monster is here too.

526
00:31:02,470 --> 00:31:03,010
Wait for me!

527
00:31:03,880 --> 00:31:04,660
Just listen to me.

528
00:31:04,680 --> 00:31:05,290
Don't touch me.

529
00:31:07,070 --> 00:31:08,250
Riyan.

530
00:31:09,160 --> 00:31:10,050
Riyan,

531
00:31:10,510 --> 00:31:12,380
could you teach me

532
00:31:12,440 --> 00:31:13,620
the Divine Brush Teleportation skill?

533
00:31:14,550 --> 00:31:16,530
Old monster, mind your own business!

534
00:31:16,680 --> 00:31:17,580
You're stealing my spotlight!

535
00:31:18,160 --> 00:31:19,900
Fox, you're truly ungrateful.

536
00:31:20,710 --> 00:31:22,490
I went out of my way to help you,

537
00:31:23,070 --> 00:31:24,380
yet you won't even say thank you.

538
00:31:25,510 --> 00:31:26,620
Mr. Yan.

539
00:31:27,470 --> 00:31:28,340
Lifei,

540
00:31:28,470 --> 00:31:30,730
we're fated to cross paths from afar.

541
00:31:31,030 --> 00:31:32,860
It'd be such a waste not to strike it rich together.

542
00:31:33,030 --> 00:31:34,180
You stinky old monster!

543
00:31:37,920 --> 00:31:38,580
Mr. Yan,

544
00:31:39,880 --> 00:31:40,730
what are you doing here?

545
00:31:41,470 --> 00:31:42,860
Lately, folks are on edge,

546
00:31:42,880 --> 00:31:43,770
and business has been slow,

547
00:31:43,990 --> 00:31:46,100
so I plan to travel overseas

548
00:31:46,680 --> 00:31:48,340
to gather material for new tales.

549
00:31:50,840 --> 00:31:51,490
Mr. Yan,

550
00:31:52,710 --> 00:31:55,100
are you also a monster?

551
00:31:58,440 --> 00:32:01,420
Anything abnormal is labeled as a monster.

552
00:32:02,030 --> 00:32:02,940
In that sense,

553
00:32:04,120 --> 00:32:05,450
we're all monsters.

554
00:32:05,750 --> 00:32:06,420
True.

555
00:32:06,960 --> 00:32:07,970
None of us fit the norm,

556
00:32:08,200 --> 00:32:09,010
so we're all monsters alike.

557
00:32:10,600 --> 00:32:11,250
Mr. Yan,

558
00:32:11,550 --> 00:32:12,290
what kind of monster are you?

559
00:32:13,710 --> 00:32:15,690
Your mastery over script spirit is peerless,

560
00:32:16,070 --> 00:32:17,490
so you must possess a semi-immortal body,

561
00:32:18,030 --> 00:32:19,970
knowing all under heaven.

562
00:32:23,550 --> 00:32:24,690
Does that mean

563
00:32:25,360 --> 00:32:26,770
all script spirits obey your will?

564
00:32:27,230 --> 00:32:28,690
No wonder you're skilled at spinning tales.

565
00:32:33,920 --> 00:32:36,340
I'm deeply grateful to all of you for your help.

566
00:32:36,550 --> 00:32:38,380
I'll lead my clansmen to Yingcui Island to settle down.

567
00:32:38,960 --> 00:32:39,730
Farewell for now.

568
00:32:42,880 --> 00:32:45,860
Yingcui Island belongs to that great bird.

569
00:32:46,600 --> 00:32:48,180
Are you its descendant?

570
00:32:49,510 --> 00:32:50,860
I'm Lu Li, leader of the Jiufeng Clan,

571
00:32:51,230 --> 00:32:52,530
half-monster.

572
00:32:54,270 --> 00:32:55,660
Yingcui Island is thousands of miles away.

573
00:32:55,990 --> 00:32:57,210
You'll struggle to travel there.

574
00:32:57,550 --> 00:32:59,530
I'll give you a ride.

575
00:33:00,880 --> 00:33:01,690
Thanks, Mr. Yan.

576
00:33:02,200 --> 00:33:02,730
Old coot,

577
00:33:03,120 --> 00:33:04,010
you're tagging along.

578
00:33:04,470 --> 00:33:06,770
I'm going overseas to find answers.

579
00:33:08,600 --> 00:33:09,210
Young man,

580
00:33:10,270 --> 00:33:10,940
come over here.

581
00:33:11,270 --> 00:33:12,530
I need a word with you.

582
00:33:26,070 --> 00:33:27,490
You've got your old memories back,

583
00:33:28,710 --> 00:33:30,340
so you know who she is, right?

584
00:33:33,310 --> 00:33:34,210
So what if I know?

585
00:33:36,600 --> 00:33:37,450
I've only ever wanted her

586
00:33:37,920 --> 00:33:39,140
from day one.

587
00:33:39,920 --> 00:33:41,210
Can you protect her?

588
00:33:42,070 --> 00:33:42,900
You just want to

589
00:33:43,600 --> 00:33:45,290
lock her up for yourself.

590
00:33:46,360 --> 00:33:47,690
Your so-called love

591
00:33:48,070 --> 00:33:49,140
is poisoning her.

592
00:33:49,470 --> 00:33:50,420
Things will be different in this life.

593
00:33:52,360 --> 00:33:53,450
She might believe you

594
00:33:54,070 --> 00:33:55,100
a few times,

595
00:33:56,920 --> 00:33:58,620
but she'll see through you eventually.

596
00:34:03,030 --> 00:34:03,730
Riyan,

597
00:34:05,230 --> 00:34:06,180
you misunderstand her.

598
00:34:08,790 --> 00:34:09,820
Lifei is far from foolish.

599
00:34:11,120 --> 00:34:12,010
At times,

600
00:34:13,110 --> 00:34:14,010
she is even wiser than I am

601
00:34:15,510 --> 00:34:16,450
and is clear about her choices.

602
00:34:23,920 --> 00:34:24,820
Mark my words.

603
00:34:25,280 --> 00:34:26,970
If she suffers even the slightest injury,

604
00:34:29,510 --> 00:34:31,050
I will hold you accountable.

605
00:34:38,590 --> 00:34:39,530
Rest assured.

606
00:34:39,960 --> 00:34:41,700
I'll protect her with all I have.

607
00:34:47,800 --> 00:34:49,170
What are you two whispering about?

608
00:34:51,440 --> 00:34:52,940
You don't want to leave me?

609
00:34:53,630 --> 00:34:55,090
When I first met you,

610
00:34:55,510 --> 00:34:56,490
you were a fool.

611
00:34:57,380 --> 00:34:58,650
Now that I'm leaving,

612
00:34:59,340 --> 00:35:00,380
you still are.

613
00:35:03,240 --> 00:35:04,860
Just say it if you'll miss me.

614
00:35:05,590 --> 00:35:06,340
Enough,

615
00:35:06,470 --> 00:35:07,130
old fox.

616
00:35:07,420 --> 00:35:08,340
Let's go.

617
00:35:08,820 --> 00:35:10,380
Young folks have their own paths to walk.

618
00:35:10,780 --> 00:35:12,530
Let's stay out of this.

619
00:35:13,670 --> 00:35:14,300
True.

620
00:35:15,190 --> 00:35:15,970
I've slept far too long.

621
00:35:16,900 --> 00:35:18,780
Time to stretch my limbs.

622
00:35:30,780 --> 00:35:31,490
Girl,

623
00:35:31,670 --> 00:35:32,700
on your way back,

624
00:35:32,780 --> 00:35:34,260
visit the East Sea's cliff inscriptions.

625
00:35:36,110 --> 00:35:37,420
Did you leave a treasure for me?

626
00:35:50,670 --> 00:35:53,050
I wonder if Lifei managed to escape.

627
00:35:54,670 --> 00:35:55,380
Don't worry.

628
00:35:56,110 --> 00:35:57,130
She'll be fine

629
00:35:57,300 --> 00:35:58,380
with Xiuyuan by her side.

630
00:36:06,820 --> 00:36:07,740
Jiao said a witness

631
00:36:08,340 --> 00:36:10,220
claimed Lifei helped the monster clan run off.

632
00:36:11,900 --> 00:36:12,820
We promised we wouldn't...

633
00:36:17,380 --> 00:36:18,940
We promised we wouldn't leave any clues.

634
00:36:19,070 --> 00:36:19,780
Who ratted them out?

635
00:36:20,150 --> 00:36:21,010
No matter who it is,

636
00:36:21,470 --> 00:36:22,860
Lifei will be in trouble if she comes back.

637
00:36:26,590 --> 00:36:27,610
Then she'd better stay away

638
00:36:28,190 --> 00:36:29,700
and lie low somewhere.

639
00:36:31,980 --> 00:36:32,650
I'll go and find her.

640
00:36:54,590 --> 00:36:56,530
Our trip begins at Mount Man by the East Sea.

641
00:36:56,940 --> 00:36:58,300
Boundless ocean spreads out.

642
00:36:58,470 --> 00:36:59,780
By Qingcheng of Wuyue Court

643
00:37:00,300 --> 00:37:02,450
and Riyan of Qingqiu.

644
00:37:03,720 --> 00:37:06,130
Riyan was actually close with Elder Qingcheng.

645
00:37:07,820 --> 00:37:09,130
I never heard this before.

646
00:37:16,110 --> 00:37:18,170
Where do you reckon Elder Qingcheng ended up later?

647
00:37:19,190 --> 00:37:20,490
My master said

648
00:37:20,820 --> 00:37:22,340
he invented the Five Turtle Technique.

649
00:37:27,900 --> 00:37:28,610
It's late.

650
00:37:29,380 --> 00:37:30,610
Let's go home.

651
00:37:47,990 --> 00:37:50,010
I figured Riyan might've felt guilty

652
00:37:50,240 --> 00:37:51,530
and left me a spirit artifact.

653
00:37:52,070 --> 00:37:53,130
Total letdown.

654
00:37:54,110 --> 00:37:54,780
Xiuyuan,

655
00:37:55,380 --> 00:37:56,420
why'd you stick around?

656
00:37:57,940 --> 00:37:58,820
Because you stayed.

657
00:38:03,340 --> 00:38:04,940
You could've gone your separate way.

658
00:38:06,240 --> 00:38:06,940
After all,

659
00:38:08,110 --> 00:38:09,860
we can't stay together forever.

660
00:38:11,150 --> 00:38:12,010
Why can't we?

661
00:38:17,510 --> 00:38:18,340
Our bond won't fade.

662
00:38:19,670 --> 00:38:20,610
We won't leave each other, living or dead.

663
00:38:35,110 --> 00:38:35,700
Lifei,

664
00:38:38,150 --> 00:38:39,420
I want to be with you forever,

665
00:38:42,420 --> 00:38:43,050
in this lifetime,

666
00:38:44,510 --> 00:38:45,340
and every next one.

667
00:38:59,550 --> 00:39:00,530
What're you talking about?

668
00:39:06,900 --> 00:39:07,650
Nothing much.

669
00:39:08,630 --> 00:39:09,450
What brings you here?

670
00:39:09,980 --> 00:39:11,610
They say you worked with the monster clan

671
00:39:11,630 --> 00:39:12,340
and broke them out of prison.

672
00:39:12,670 --> 00:39:13,860
Don't head back to Duanming City.

673
00:39:14,550 --> 00:39:15,820
I covered our tracks the whole trip.

674
00:39:16,820 --> 00:39:17,740
Who ratted her out?

675
00:39:18,340 --> 00:39:18,900
No clue.

676
00:39:19,240 --> 00:39:20,090
The elders plan

677
00:39:20,110 --> 00:39:21,380
to question Lifei severely.

678
00:39:25,190 --> 00:39:25,940
This is bad.

679
00:39:26,380 --> 00:39:27,900
Hide out with me at Xingzheng Hall for now.

680
00:39:28,590 --> 00:39:29,820
Running off now

681
00:39:30,590 --> 00:39:31,940
would make me look guilty on the run.

682
00:39:33,820 --> 00:39:35,170
I didn't slip up at all last night.

683
00:39:35,190 --> 00:39:36,260
I'll just deny it.

684
00:39:36,940 --> 00:39:37,860
It won't be easy to get away with.

685
00:39:38,420 --> 00:39:39,530
Cuixuan and my uncle

686
00:39:39,780 --> 00:39:41,010
will see right through our lies.

687
00:39:41,460 --> 00:39:43,570
What if they torture you to talk?

688
00:39:43,900 --> 00:39:45,050
They wouldn't do that.

689
00:39:45,720 --> 00:39:47,450
Those sect elders

690
00:39:47,780 --> 00:39:50,170
torture a weak girl

691
00:39:50,190 --> 00:39:51,170
to get a fake confession?

692
00:39:51,380 --> 00:39:52,570
That's cruel.

693
00:39:53,190 --> 00:39:54,220
And it'll be very embarrassing

694
00:39:54,670 --> 00:39:56,050
if everyone finds out.

695
00:39:59,070 --> 00:39:59,860
But what if they do?

696
00:40:00,550 --> 00:40:01,420
We'll team up

697
00:40:01,550 --> 00:40:02,490
and get through anything.

698
00:40:12,820 --> 00:40:14,420
I hunted monster beasts all night

699
00:40:14,510 --> 00:40:15,530
and did my job properly.

700
00:40:15,670 --> 00:40:16,900
How do I suddenly become a demon spy?

701
00:40:18,190 --> 00:40:18,820
Mr. Luo,

702
00:40:19,190 --> 00:40:20,860
we met last night, didn't we?

703
00:40:21,240 --> 00:40:22,530
I saw you last night,

704
00:40:23,190 --> 00:40:24,420
but you reeked

705
00:40:24,630 --> 00:40:25,820
of evil spiritual energy back then.

706
00:40:27,820 --> 00:40:28,820
That just means

707
00:40:29,030 --> 00:40:30,820
I was fighting monster beasts hard.

708
00:40:33,670 --> 00:40:35,010
Lifei stuck with the group

709
00:40:35,510 --> 00:40:36,490
and hunted monster beasts

710
00:40:36,980 --> 00:40:37,740
straight through till morning.

711
00:40:38,630 --> 00:40:39,820
You two have long been close friends.

712
00:40:39,940 --> 00:40:40,740
You might be lying

713
00:40:40,940 --> 00:40:41,820
to cover for one another.

714
00:40:43,030 --> 00:40:43,740
Qin,

715
00:40:44,420 --> 00:40:46,300
you mean we're covering each other,

716
00:40:47,030 --> 00:40:48,820
and that makes me a spy, too?

717
00:40:52,980 --> 00:40:55,450
I followed the evil spiritual energy last night

718
00:40:55,940 --> 00:40:57,300
and was jumped halfway.

719
00:40:57,900 --> 00:40:58,940
Jiang Lifei's the one

720
00:40:59,340 --> 00:41:00,490
who attacked me.

721
00:41:01,980 --> 00:41:02,740
Qin,

722
00:41:02,980 --> 00:41:04,380
you've hated me ever since what happened

723
00:41:04,420 --> 00:41:05,420
at Lilie Valley.

724
00:41:05,940 --> 00:41:07,130
If you want to get even,

725
00:41:07,240 --> 00:41:08,340
fight me fair and square.

726
00:41:09,070 --> 00:41:11,130
Quit stabbing me in the back.

727
00:41:11,460 --> 00:41:12,340
You're disgracing Wuyue Court

728
00:41:12,380 --> 00:41:13,490
and Elder Cuixuan.

729
00:41:13,720 --> 00:41:14,130
You!

730
00:41:14,150 --> 00:41:14,970
Yangling,

731
00:41:15,820 --> 00:41:17,970
you said she attacked you.

732
00:41:19,380 --> 00:41:20,420
Got any evidence?

733
00:41:20,900 --> 00:41:21,610
I'm sure

734
00:41:22,240 --> 00:41:24,300
that energy is definitely hers.

735
00:41:26,510 --> 00:41:27,380
Qin,

736
00:41:27,980 --> 00:41:29,050
I didn't know

737
00:41:29,470 --> 00:41:30,740
you thought about me so much

738
00:41:30,780 --> 00:41:31,490
that you see me

739
00:41:31,510 --> 00:41:32,420
in everyone now.

740
00:41:33,720 --> 00:41:35,340
She's the demon spy.

741
00:41:41,070 --> 00:41:41,650
It's her!

742
00:41:41,940 --> 00:41:43,450
She dressed up like one of us from the Wanxian Sect

743
00:41:43,720 --> 00:41:45,010
and knocked us out with drugs.

744
00:41:45,420 --> 00:41:46,530
Did you actually see me drug you?

745
00:41:47,150 --> 00:41:48,740
No, we didn't.

746
00:41:49,470 --> 00:41:50,340
But right after you walked past,

747
00:41:50,550 --> 00:41:51,380
we passed out.

748
00:41:52,460 --> 00:41:54,300
You were all lazing around

749
00:41:54,340 --> 00:41:55,010
and sleeping on duty.

750
00:41:55,030 --> 00:41:55,820
That's why the monster beasts got away.

751
00:41:55,860 --> 00:41:56,420
Now

752
00:41:56,820 --> 00:41:57,490
you're scared of taking the blame,

753
00:41:57,590 --> 00:41:58,380
so you lie and pin it on me?

754
00:41:59,150 --> 00:41:59,820
Well... I...

755
00:42:00,590 --> 00:42:01,490
Speaking of which,

756
00:42:01,720 --> 00:42:03,220
you really did have

757
00:42:03,240 --> 00:42:04,970
our Wanxian Sect outer robe on that night.

758
00:42:05,300 --> 00:42:06,090
Why was that?

759
00:42:10,460 --> 00:42:11,260
This is all on me.

760
00:42:13,470 --> 00:42:14,530
Lifei only took

761
00:42:14,720 --> 00:42:15,780
such a risky action to visit

762
00:42:17,340 --> 00:42:18,340
my uncle for my sake.

763
00:42:18,470 --> 00:42:20,090
You're from Wuyue Court.

764
00:42:20,240 --> 00:42:21,340
What were you doing

765
00:42:21,720 --> 00:42:23,700
visiting Mr. Xuanshan late at night?

766
00:42:31,550 --> 00:42:32,970
I wanted to form a cultivation partnership with Lifei,

767
00:42:33,720 --> 00:42:35,010
but I feared that my uncle wouldn't agree.

768
00:42:37,340 --> 00:42:38,450
She panicked

769
00:42:38,860 --> 00:42:40,050
and went straight in to ask why.

770
00:42:42,050 --> 00:42:42,300
[The Eternal Fragrance]

771
00:42:42,300 --> 00:42:44,560
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

772
00:42:55,800 --> 00:42:59,480
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

773
00:42:59,800 --> 00:43:02,480
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

774
00:43:02,560 --> 00:43:05,800
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

775
00:43:05,800 --> 00:43:09,080
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

776
00:43:09,200 --> 00:43:13,080
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

777
00:43:13,360 --> 00:43:16,560
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

778
00:43:16,720 --> 00:43:22,800
♪No calamity can rival the lingering thread of a fragrance♪

779
00:43:23,080 --> 00:43:27,200
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

780
00:43:27,480 --> 00:43:30,160
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

781
00:43:30,360 --> 00:43:32,280
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

782
00:43:32,400 --> 00:43:36,720
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

783
00:43:36,880 --> 00:43:40,720
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

784
00:43:41,080 --> 00:43:44,080
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

785
00:43:44,160 --> 00:43:50,280
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

786
00:43:50,480 --> 00:43:54,200
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

787
00:44:07,440 --> 00:44:11,200
♪I trade the highest heaven and endless clouds♪

788
00:44:11,400 --> 00:44:14,200
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

789
00:44:14,280 --> 00:44:17,680
♪Pierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on♪

790
00:44:17,680 --> 00:44:21,000
♪Yet I remain silent♪

791
00:44:21,160 --> 00:44:25,000
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

792
00:44:25,160 --> 00:44:28,360
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

793
00:44:28,600 --> 00:44:34,440
♪The grand chapter is rewritten, startling the whole world♪

794
00:44:35,000 --> 00:44:38,920
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

795
00:44:39,200 --> 00:44:41,960
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

796
00:44:42,160 --> 00:44:44,000
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

797
00:44:44,160 --> 00:44:48,360
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

798
00:44:48,600 --> 00:44:52,480
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

799
00:44:52,720 --> 00:44:55,760
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

800
00:44:55,960 --> 00:45:02,680
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

801
00:45:02,720 --> 00:45:06,680
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

802
00:45:06,920 --> 00:45:09,680
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

803
00:45:09,800 --> 00:45:11,720
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds♪

804
00:45:11,880 --> 00:45:16,160
♪Break through the waves; the heart's ocean knows no shore♪

805
00:45:16,360 --> 00:45:20,200
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

806
00:45:20,440 --> 00:45:23,560
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

807
00:45:23,600 --> 00:45:29,600
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water and falling petals♪

808
00:45:30,000 --> 00:45:34,360
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪

